description: Demolition of the existing building at Station Road and redevelopment to provide a part 4, 27, 32 and 42 storey block with basement comprising 370 residential units and ancillary facilities retail (Class A1-A3), office (Class B1) and all other incidental works. Recladding of Cranbrook Road properties. Improvements to Bodgers Arcade (Summary)
decision_conditions:
The development hereby permitted shall be begun no later than the  expiration of three years from the date of this permission.

Reason: In order to comply with the requirements of Section 91 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990.
site_name: Development At 1 To 15 And 17 Station Road And 16 To 26
